{
  "stem": "14060.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I thought this was a highly interesting custom, because these customs were not everywhere kept.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "These were individual customs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Where they originate from, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The only thing-- after the war, I-- since I lived in England, I've been to Gibraltar.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there's a surviving community of about 500 years old.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I found, interestingly, some customs which were very similar to the ones which we had.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I assume the reason for it must be that they-- the descendants of people who were chased out of Spain or Portugal and came back to Gibraltar, [INAUDIBLE] maybe others after the Inquisition, moved to the east, obviously they did to Italy, all the way to Constantinople, which is today Turkey.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And also to our part-- certainly Holland, Germany, and then filtering more to the east.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I presume it has something to do with it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now, so therefore, what happened was, the person died.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Could be the head of the family or even a wife or a child.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They had no chance to get buried anywhere else but only in the cemetery of the community, because nobody else would have touched them, not even the other Jewish community, for no money in the world.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This was an implied agreement.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You don't take refugees over, because for financial reasons, they want to run away from their responsibility.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was down to the chevra kadisha president and the treasurer to negotiate, during the time of sadness, when somebody just lost somebody overnight, that they had to pay up all the money they owed.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And otherwise, there was no burial.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, this may not be very kind.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
